                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(center)\"><placeName>Montreal</placeName> list of subscribers to</p>\n            <p rend=\"align(center)\">\n                <hi rend=\"underline\">the Jewish Advocate</hi>\n            </p>\n            <list type=\"simple\">\n                <head/>\n                <item>\n                    <persName>J H Joseph</persName>\n                </item>\n                <item>The <persName>Misses Joseph</persName></item>\n                <item>\n                    <persName>D Moss</persName>\n                </item>\n                <item>\n                    <persName>G D Ascher</persName>\n                </item>\n                <item>\n                    <persName>E Mendels</persName>\n                </item>\n                <item>\n                    <persName>E Benjamin</persName>\n                </item>\n                <item>\n                    <persName>N Saunders</persName>\n                </item>\n                <item>\n                    <persName>J Piddian<add>?</add></persName>\n                </item>\n                <item>\n                    <persName>E Moss</persName>\n                </item>\n                <item>\n                    <persName>R Kostosk</persName>\n                </item>\n                <item>\n                    <persName role=\"author\">Abraham de Sola</persName>\n                </item>\n            </list>\n            <p\n                rend=\"The following lines are written on the right side of the page, to the right of the list of subscribers\"\n                >I retain the original<lb/> signatures on the circular<lb/> for which I have<lb/>\n                written some words of<lb/> recommendation because<lb/> I dare say I shall\n                obtain<lb/> more; and it may<lb/> be useful when<lb/> payments are due.<lb/> Say\n                    <add>?</add> two subscribers at present<lb/> for I think I may sign for<lb/>\n                <persName>Mr J. Samuel</persName>, not yet seen.</p>\n            <pb n=\"Envelope\"/>\n            <p>Paid</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">The <addressee>Rev. Isaac Leeser</addressee></p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">\n                <placeName>371 Walnut Street</placeName>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(3)\">\n                <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(4)\">\n                <placeName>Pa</placeName>\n            </p>\n        </body>\n    </text>\n</TEI>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3xp6vp8q/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
